To construct the LET spectra, data is grouped in M bins (each 1 keV/µm, in silicon). In this case the dose rate can be calculated by summing over all the LET bins (M) the products of the average LET in each bin by the counts in the same bin:6\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
