				\begin{document}$$Dose\,rate\,(\frac{nGy}{s})=1.6\,\frac{4\pi }{GF{\rm{\Delta }}T}\,\sum _{i=1}^{M}{C}_{i}LE{T}_{i}$$\end{document}Doserate(nGys)=1.64πGFΔT∑i=1MCiLETiwhere C
i is the counts in the ith bin and it has been considered that ρH2O = 1 g/cm3.

